<div type="content">
<ab>Edler lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr edel
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>lantgr<ex>af</ex></expan>
<expan>Johanns<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>Lewchtemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und ob icht prüch
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>zweyu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>zwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ewr <expan>beid<ex>er</ex></expan> seit
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan>, daz die
                            <expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ab <expan>gienge<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        sehen wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>; und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        ewr edel <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz uns der
                                <expan>vorg<ex>ena</ex>nt<ex>e</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> der lantgraf <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        mass niht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>punden</expan> ist, daz wir sein mechtig sein,
                        zu recht zu <expan>stell<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell sust lieb
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>ri</ex></expan> et Pauli.</ab>
